# This is a list of my preferred apps used for each activity on the comp

## IMAGES
view from the CLI                   :: feh
view for minimal edit               :: xnviewmp
edit raster image                   :: GIMP
edit vector image                   :: Inkscape or kritta
diagrams                            :: dia, pencil

## TEXT
CLI editor                          :: vim, Doom(emacs)
rich text                           :: LibreOffice [ Alt L ]

## CLIPBOARD
clipboard manager                   :: Klipper

## ORGANISING
emacs                               :: doom [ Alt E ]
task manager                        :: org-mode (using Doom emacs)

## EMAIL
laptop                              :: Thunderbird [ Alt T ]
webmail                             :: gmail, gandhi, microsoft, yahoo, eircom

## TERMINAL
emulator                            :: Terminator [ Alt N ]
shell                               :: zsh
zsh add-on framework                :: oh-my-zsh (to be reassessed)
text search                         :: rg
find files                          :: fd
command reminder                    :: cheat
websearch engine                    :: ddgr
system process monitor              :: htop
file manager                        :: ranger (to access in vim: ,f )
promt display                       :: powerline
package manager                     :: pamac, pacman
multiplexer                         :: tmux
dropdown terminal                   :: yakuake (F12)

## snapshot creator
manjaro                             :: timeshift

# DISPLAY
night color temp                    :: Night Color Control, Redshift

## DESKTOP ENVIRONMENT
manjaro                             :: KDE Plasma

## SCREEN CAPTURE
yakuake (F12)                       :: spectacles


## APP SWITCHER
linux                               :: jumpapp (with keyboard shortcuts - see custom shortcuts), synapse ([SPC] )  


## PERSONAL KNOWLEDGE MANAGER       
Knowledge storage                   :: zim-wiki [ Alt Z ]

## READERS
PDF                                 :: zathura, okular
markdown                            :: ?? typora, markdown-git, Marktext
ebooks                              :: ?? calibre, fbookreader

## WEB-BROWSER
GUI                                 :: Firefox [ Alt B ], Chromium [ Alt C ]
CLI                                 :: w3m

## TEXT EXPANDER
python                              :: autokey [ Alt A ]

## CONTAINERIZATION
linux                               :: Docker

## VERSION CONTROL
guess what                          :: git
web repo                            :: (currently) github 

## DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT
linux                               :: for Ubuntu Server: Multipass

## COLOR PICKER
linux                               :: pick

## PYTHON PACKAGE MANAGER
linux                               :: pip3

## PASSWORD MANAGER
linux                               :: own - zim-wiki, passin, passout

## DATABASE
linux                               :: sqlite

## TUNNELLING SERVICE
linux                               :: ngrok, tunnelto

## WINDOWS MANAGER
linux                               :: KDE 

## VIM NAVIGATION
